thumbnail.caption: Now on shelves, fans can collect three Hawaiian-inspired limited-edition SPAM® brand cans featuring artwork from the beloved movie. The collectible cans contain the same classic SPAM® product that has been a staple in Hawaiian cuisine for generations. Available at major retailers nationwide, these island treasures are expected to sell quickly — collect them all while supplies last!
